Description:  Provides R bindings to the 'Hoedown' 'Markdown' rendering library
   (https://github.com/hoedown/hoedown). 'Markdown' is a plain-text formatting
   syntax that can be converted to 'XHTML' or other formats. See
   http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown for more information about 'Markdown'.
